# RUNNING SYSTEM

## Setup
You first need to go through the README and ge things setup.
You will need to make sure that the laptop is set as the ros master
and all of the networking is connected.

## Local Machine
run a roscore: `roscore`
launch camera capture: `rosrun usb_cam usb_cam_node`

## Remote Machine
launch `rosrun image_view image_view image:=usb_cam/image_raw _image_transport:=theora _window_name:=remote-video`
then make the screen full screen: `wmctrl -r remote-video -b add,fullscreen
